	heroSubhead={`Maybe you left. Maybe you were never in. Maybe the God you heard about — distant, angry, keeping score — just never seemed real, or kind, or worth it. That's fair. But what if that God was never the real One? You're invited to read for yourself and decide. No pressure, no membership, no agenda.`}
