	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're a skeptic, a doubter, or somewhere on the long road out of the faith you were raised in — this is for you, exactly as you are.</strong> Maybe you've searched "is God real," "does God exist," "deconstructing faith," or "why I left the church." Maybe you'd call yourself spiritual but not religious, or done with religion entirely. Plenty of people walked away for honest reasons — hypocrisy, judgment, real harm, or a God who sounded more like an angry rule-maker than anything worth knowing. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free, privately, on your own terms. It asks one honest question: what is the Bible really about? And its answer might surprise you — beneath the religion and the rules, there is a Father who actually loves you, with no strings. You don't have to believe anything to read it. You just have to be curious enough to look.`}
