		{ ref: `Romans 8:15`, slug: `romans`, ch: 8, text: `You did not receive a spirit that makes you a slave to fear again; you received the Spirit of belonging, by whom we cry out, "Father."`, note: `If faith was handed to you as fear, this says fear was never the point — belonging was.` },
