		{ ref: `Romans 8:38-39`, slug: `romans`, ch: 8, text: `I am convinced that nothing — not death, not life, not the past, not the future, nothing in all creation — can separate us from the love of the Father.`, note: `If you left, this says the love didn't. The distance you feel was never on His side.` },
