	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `Meet the God of the text, not the caricature`, bodyHtml: `It's easy to reject a cartoon — an angry rule-maker, a list of demands, the version someone weaponized against you. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does, from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. Read the actual source and decide for yourself who God is — not who you were told He was.` },
		{ heading: `Free, private, and no church required`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app, no membership, no one watching. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — quietly, on your own, on your own terms. You don't have to set foot in a building or tell a soul. Just read, or listen, and decide.` },
		{ heading: `It takes your doubt seriously`, bodyHtml: `This isn't a debate to win you. If you have honest questions, start with <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or, if you ever want to try talking to God yourself, a plain-language <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> with zero formulas. No pressure, no performance — just an open door.` },
